# HOW TO GET API KEYS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# MONGODB:
#   1. Visit https://mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
#   2. Create free account and cluster
#   3. Click "Connect" > "Connect your application"
#   4. Copy connection string
#
# CLERK:
#   1. Visit https://clerk.com and sign up
#   2. Create new application
#   3. Copy API keys from Dashboard
#
# IMAGEKIT:
#   1. Visit https://imagekit.io and sign up
#   2. Go to Dashboard > Developer Options
#   3. Copy Public Key, Private Key, and URL Endpoint
#
# GIPHY:
#   1. Visit https://developers.giphy.com
#   2. Create app and get API key
#   3. Free tier available
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#   5. Copy connection string
#   6. Replace <username> and <password> with your credentials
#   7. Paste into MONGO_URI above
#
# CLERK_SECRET_KEY (optional):
#   1. Visit https://dashboard.clerk.com
#   2. Create account and application
#   3. Go to API Keys section
#   4. Copy Secret Key
#   5. Paste into CLERK_SECRET_KEY above
#
